reviewText: This is a great video biography of one of Hollywwod's greatest and versatile actors Robert Wagner. It's a must see!!!!!!!!!!!

GREAT BIO.  SCENES FROM NORTH BY NORTHWEST, TO CATCH A THIEF, HIS GIRL FRIDAY AND MUCH MORE.  ALSO HOME MOVIE FOOTAGE OF GRANT RELAXING AT HOME.  BONUS - BEHIND THE SCENES WHILE MAKING SOME OF HIS MOST MEMORABLE FILMS.
